## System memory/cpu
check system <%= node[:ec2][:public_hostname] %>
  if loadavg (15min) > <%= (node[:cpu][:total].to_f / 1.5).round -%> for 10 cycles then alert
  if memory usage > 98% for 10 cycles then alert
  if cpu usage (wait) > 10% for 10 cycles then alert
  group host

## Disk
check device root-70 with path / every 4 cycles
  if space usage > 70% then alert
  group disk

check device root-90 with path / every 4 cycles
  if space usage > 90% then alert
  group disk

